OL,3,C'Significant changes and improvements'
OL,4,Cmade to hospital since Letby's attacks
OL,6,FSignificant changes and improvements
OL,7,Fhave been made at a hospital where
OL,8,FLucy Letby murdered babies, its Chief
OL,9,FExecutive has told a public inquiry.
OL,11,FJane Tomkinson said the Countess of
OL,12,FChester Hospital is more open to
OL,13,Flistening to staff concerns and access
OL,14,Fto insulin has changed.
OL,16,FShe added she was "truly sorry" on the
OL,17,Fhospital's behalf to the families of
OL,18,Fchildren who were killed or harmed by
OL,19,Fthe former neonatal nurse in 2015 and
OL,20,F2016.
