OL,3,C'Significant changes and improvements'
OL,4,Cmade to hospital since Letby's attacks
OL,6,FGiving evidence at the Thirlwall
OL,7,FInquiry into the events surrounding
OL,8,FLetby's crimes, Ms Tomkinson said: "I
OL,9,Fam really clear that there have been
OL,10,Fsignificant changes and improvements
OL,11,Fin the organisation between the period
OL,12,Fin question and the current day.
OL,14,F"The changes are very numerous but I
OL,15,Fwould hope today that the response to
OL,16,Fanything like the events from 2015
OL,17,Fonwards would be handled completely
OL,18,Fdifferently from ward to board."
