OL,3,C'Significant changes and improvements'
OL,4,Cmade to hospital since Letby's attacks
OL,6,FMs Tomkinson joined the hospital trust
OL,7,Fin December 2022 as acting Chief
OL,8,FExecutive and took up the post
OL,9,Fpermanently in February 2024.
OL,11,FThe parents of Letby's victims have
OL,12,Fcriticised the former senior
OL,13,Fmanagement over claims they ignored
OL,14,Fwarnings from consultant
OL,15,Fpaediatricians about a potential link
OL,16,Fto her and babies dying or
OL,17,Fdeteriorating.
