OL,3,C'Significant changes and improvements'
OL,4,Cmade to hospital since Letby's attacks
OL,6,FEx-Chief Executive Tony Chambers
OL,7,Fpreviously told the inquiry it was
OL,8,F"outrageous" to suggest he had sought
OL,9,Fto stall a police investigation at
OL,10,Fevery stage and had wanted to ruin the
OL,11,Fcareers of two of the senior medics
OL,12,Fwho brought the matter to his
OL,13,Fattention.
OL,15,FOn Monday, Ms Tomkinson said there was
OL,16,Fnow a "clear way" for employees to
OL,17,Fescalate concerns about patient safety.
OL,19,FShe said: "We are much more open to
OL,20,Flistening to our staff."
