OL,3,C'Significant changes and improvements'
OL,4,Cmade to hospital since Letby's attacks
OL,6,FShe added that the method of staff
OL,7,Faccess to insulin had since changed
OL,8,Fwith a "clear audit trail" provided by
OL,9,Fa "bespoke swipe card that is
OL,10,Fabsolutely aligned to an individual
OL,11,Fstaff member".
OL,13,FLetby was convicted of attempting to
OL,14,Fmurder two baby boys by poisoning them
OL,15,Fwith insulin.
OL,17,FDuring her attack spree, insulin was
OL,18,Fkept on the unit in a locked fridge
OL,19,Fbut keys to it were passed among staff
OL,20,Fas and when needed.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@ZO]qD@COUsD@MO]
