OL,4,Cmade to hospital since Letby's attacks
OL,6,FMs Tomkinson added: "The impact of the
OL,7,Fharms and deaths will never leave this
OL,8,Fhospital and rightly so, we will never
OL,9,Fforget it.
OL,11,F"But people want to focus on the
OL,12,Ffuture, learn from the past but
OL,13,Freshape the future in a different way
OL,14,Fand certainly the feedback I have had
OL,15,Ffor that is myself and the new
OL,16,Fexecutive team are making a
OL,17,Fsignificant difference at pace on
OL,18,Fdelivery and culture."
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@AOUzD@VO]
