OL,3,C'Significant changes and improvements'
OL,4,Cmade to hospital since Letby's attacks
OL,6,FShe told the inquiry she was "really
OL,7,Fpushing" for the reinstatement of
OL,8,FLevel 2 status to its neonatal unit so
OL,9,Fthat high dependency care could be
OL,10,Fprovided to infants.
OL,12,FMs Tomkinson agreed with the
OL,13,Fsuggestion by Richard Baker KC,
OL,14,Frepresenting families of Letby's
OL,15,Fvictims, that the executive team in
OL,16,F2015 and 2016 did not follow various
OL,17,Fpolicies and processes including those
OL,18,Fon duty of candour and whistleblowing.
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@HO]
